$PAR
Assume \({\bf u}_4\) is not a linear combination of 
\(\lbrace{{\bf u}_1, {\bf u}_2, {\bf u}_3 }\rbrace\).
$PAR
Select the best statement.
$BR
\{ $mc->print_a() \}

